snippet: Much-travelled striker Carlos Tevez is set to leave Boca Juniors for Shanghai Shenhua in the New Year, Argentine media reports said on Friday....
lead_paragraph: Much-travelled striker Carlos Tevez is set to leave Boca Juniors for Shanghai Shenhua in the New Year, Argentine media reports said on Friday.

headline.main: Tevez Set to Leave Boca in Big-Money Move to China
headline.print_headline: Tevez Set to Leave Boca in Big-Money Move to China
